HEADWORD: Devoted
<hw>De*vot"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Consecrated to a purpose;
strongly attached; zealous; devout; <as>as, a <ex>devoted</ex>
admirer</as>.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>De*vot"ed*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos>
-- <wf>De*vot"ed*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Devotee</ent>⟦br⟧
